# Service Ownership Boundary

- **Codex owns** extraction, normalization, and reusable summary/detection payloads.
- **Lint owns** policy rules, reporting semantics, and preflight workflow orchestration.
- **Loupe owns** rendering, visual inspection UI, and display interactions.
- Keep Codex rule-agnostic; never hardcode customer pass/fail policy in this repo.
- For offshoots (Forge, Trap, Impose, Marks, etc.), map each feature to one owner layer and integrate by contract, not duplicated logic.
